narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: There were adequate resources at our disposal, and the instructor was approachable and helpful overall. It was an enjoyable and challenging course.
This question is not really applicable to the course.
Facilities are top-notch. Although, there was a weird timing glitch on the projector which resulted in it automatically shutting down during the middle of class, a bit of an inconvenience.
